° Total time is taken from the monk´s timetable (total time from pet only shows the last riposte i think)<br>
° Assuming a base regenration of 30hp per tick while in pet hold mode (reg must be in effect then as the Air pet casted Invisbility on itself while a friend was killing it):<br>
<br>
<br>
Enjoy &gt;&gt;<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Monster Summoning 3</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/520013139003-001/ms3hp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Time: 48sec<br>
Reg: (48/6)x30 = 240hp<br>
Total HP: 3489 - 240 = 3249 ~ 3250hp<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Greater Voc: Earth</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/520013139003-001/earth57hp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Time: 47sec<br>
Reg: (~48/6)x30 = 240hp<br>
Total HP: 3480 - 240 = 3240 ~ 3250hp<br>
<br>
I think Earth and MS3 both have the same HPs.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Greater Voc: Water</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/520013139003-001/water60hp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Time: 36sec<br>
Reg: (36/6)x30 = 180hp<br>
Total HP: 2854 - 180 = 2674 ~ 2650-2670hp<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Greater Voc: Air</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/520013139003-001/air59hp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Time: 20sec<br>
Reg: (20/6)x30 = 100hp<br>
Total HP: 2733 - 100 = 2633 ~ 2650hp <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Epic</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/520013139003-001/epichp.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
Time: 56sec<br>
Reg: (56/6)x30 = 280hp<br>
Total HP: 4257 - 280 = 3977 ~ 4000hp <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
