<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Summary:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Monster Summoning 3 - 3250hp<br>
Greater Voc: Earth - 3250hp<br>
Greater Voc: Water - 2650hp<br>
Greater Voc: Air - 2650hp<br>
Epic - 4000hp<br>
